 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>在MySQL-python-1.2.5源码包根目录下执行安装命令：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># python setup.py install&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>出现以下信息：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">error: command ‘gcc’ failed with exit status 1&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="解决方法" class="heading-element">&lt;span>解决方法&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>在安装MySQLdb前安装以下依赖库：&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>定制CentOS 6.4自动化安装ISO镜像光盘</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20130323-%E5%AE%9A%E5%88%B6centos-6.4%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85iso%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%85%89%E7%9B%98/</link><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2013 14:22:07 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20130323-%E5%AE%9A%E5%88%B6centos-6.4%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85iso%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E5%85%89%E7%9B%98/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/linux/unix/">Linux/Unix</category><description>&lt;p>和朋友今天正好聊到CentOS的自动化安装光盘制作问题，就顺便把自己之前的测试过程发出来。希望能够帮到大家。
直接发下自己之前做的时候的工作记录了，因为是工作中使用，添加了一些所需的软件包之类的东西，其实您也完全可以自由发挥，直接装完系统，一个优化好的LNMP等等众多软件都已经安装好了的系统也是完全可能的，想想网上的那些一键安装的ISO&amp;hellip;
所以大家加油哦！后期我也会完善本篇文章的具体注释的。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>让Centos支持打包、解压RAR文件包</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20120611-%E8%AE%A9centos%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8Brar%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%8C%85/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Jun 2012 11:51:46 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20120611-%E8%AE%A9centos%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85%E8%A7%A3%E5%8E%8Brar%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%8C%85/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/linux/unix/">Linux/Unix</category><description>&lt;p>有些朋友购买了vps后由于他是从原来的win主机搬迁过来，备份打包的数据是rar格式的，那在CentOS下怎么解压呢？&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Google一下，找到解决办法：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget http://www.rarsoft.com/rar/rarlinux-3.9.3.tar.gz
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">tar -xvf rarlinux-3.9.3.tar.gz
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> rar
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">make&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>看见下面这些信息就是安装成功了&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mkdir -p /wp-content/local/bin
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mkdir -p /wp-content/local/lib
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cp rar unrar /wp-content/local/bin
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cp rarfiles.lst /etc
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cp default.sfx /wp-content/local/lib&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>但有的时候在运行命令rar时,出现下面这个问题:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
